## livecheck.regex latest_[join [lrange [split ${version} .] 0 1] .]_is_(\\d+(?:\\.\\d+)*)

livecheck.type  regex
livecheck.url   http://www.cpan.org/src
livecheck.regex {perl-(5\.14\.\d)\.}
